Indian Oil Seeks to Buy Crude Oil for December Loading in Tender

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-10-07T11:46:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/indian-oil-seeks-to-buy-crude-oil-for-december-loading-in-tender.html
Indian Oil Corp., the country’s
biggest refiner, issued a tender seeking to buy low-sulfur crude
oil loading in December, according to official documents
obtained by Bloomberg News.  Last month, the company bought 7 million barrels of West
African crude for loading in November via two tenders.  Details of the company’s requirements are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
